          <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">two</NUMEX> motifs of greater than <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">20</NUMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">residues</ENAMEX>, with a
          probability of chance occurrence in these <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">proteins</ENAMEX> less
          than <NUMEX TYPE="PERCENT">10 -18</NUMEX>(<ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">Fig</ENAMEX>. <NUMEX TYPE="CARDINAL">5</NUMEX>). In addition to the similar
