          case, the bacterial RAD52-like <ENAMEX TYPE="SUBSTANCE">protein</ENAMEX> from a <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Shiga</ENAMEX> toxin
          encoding temperate phage is fused to an extreme
          C-terminal fragment that is nearly identical to the
